 Per-user Tor hidden service setup + embedded minimal HTTP server (no root required)
 Compile: cc -std=c11 -Wall -Wextra -O2 -o user_onion_embedded_web user_onion_embedded_web.c
 Run: ./user_onion_embedded_web
*/

